      <div class="team-sup-title">Backed By</div>
      <div class="team-title">The ASPN Performance Team</div>
      <div class="team-text">
        Empowering your performance with the knowledge and expertise of industry leaders, combining cutting-edge
        strategies and proven methods.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="team-fotos">
