          </div>

          <div class="back-team-bottom">
            <div class="back-team-text">
              For over a decade, Jake has been the go-to coach for some of the world’s most elite athletes, including Cy Young Award winners, NBA champions, and MMA World Champions. His deep expertise in human performance, recovery, and mental optimization has helped athletes excel at the highest levels of competition. Now, Jake is leveraging that unmatched knowledge to help everyday high performers achieve their full potential.
